      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国说，即使俄罗斯列出条款，黑海休战也同意了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰同意在黑海停火，尽管克里姆林宫表示，其参与将取决于一系列先决条件，包括制裁救济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚宣布减税，选举前预算的回扣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚左翼政府在选举前的预算中揭示了减税和其他甜味剂，旨在缓解选民的生活成本，并帮助赢得总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）的第二任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
